<p><br />
<strong>Please List your Daily Availability to Mentor Below. </strong></p>
<p>If you are hired through Work Study, you must be available to mentor at least 2 days/week. <strong>Almost all sites host BUILD after school between 3:30-5:30pm, 3-5pm, or 2:30-4pm</strong>. There may be a very limited number of daytime mentoring positions available.</p>
